Here's a modern layout XML for an eFootball-style game interface using ConstraintLayout:

xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<androidx.constraintlayout.widget.ConstraintLayout 
    xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:background="#1A1A1A">

    <!-- Game Field Container -->
    <FrameLayout
        android:id="@+id/game_field_container"
        android:layout_width="0dp"
        android:layout_height="0dp"
        android:background="@drawable/field_background"
        app:layout_constraintTop_toTopOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintBottom_toBottomOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintStart_toStartOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent">

        <!-- Game elements will be added programmatically -->
    </FrameLayout>

    <!-- Top HUD -->
    <LinearLayout
        android:id="@+id/top_hud"
        android:layout_width="0dp"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:orientation="horizontal"
        android:padding="12dp"
        app:layout_constraintTop_toTopOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintStart_toStartOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent">

        <!-- Team 1 -->
        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="0dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_weight="1"
            android:orientation="horizontal"
            android:gravity="center_vertical">

            <ImageView
                android:layout_width="32dp"
                android:layout_height="32dp"
                android:src="@drawable/team1_logo"
                android:layout_marginEnd="8dp"/>

            <TextView
                android:id="@+id/team1_name"
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:text="BARCELONA"
                android:textColor="#FFFFFF"
                android:textSize="14sp"
                android:textStyle="bold"/>

        </LinearLayout>

        <!-- Match Info -->
        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:orientation="vertical"
            android:gravity="center">

            <TextView
                android:id="@+id/match_time"
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:text="45'"
                android:textColor="#FFFFFF"
                android:textSize="18sp"
                android:textStyle="bold"/>

            <LinearLayout
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_marginTop="4dp">

                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/team1_score"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:text="2"
                    android:textColor="#FFFFFF"
                    android:textSize="24sp"
                    android:textStyle="bold"/>

                <TextView
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:text=" - "
                    android:textColor="#AAAAAA"
                    android:textSize="24sp"
                    android:layout_marginHorizontal="8dp"/>

                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/team2_score"
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:text="1"
                    android:textColor="#FFFFFF"
                    android:textSize="24sp"
                    android:textStyle="bold"/>
            </LinearLayout>
        </LinearLayout>

        <!-- Team 2 -->
        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="0dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_weight="1"
            android:orientation="horizontal"
            android:gravity="center_vertical|end">

            <TextView
                android:id="@+id/team2_name"
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:text="REAL MADRID"
                android:textColor="#FFFFFF"
                android:textSize="14sp"
                android:textStyle="bold"
                android:layout_marginEnd="8dp"/>

            <ImageView
                android:layout_width="32dp"
                android:layout_height="32dp"
                android:src="@drawable/team2_logo"/>
        </LinearLayout>
    </LinearLayout>

    <!-- Player Name Display -->
    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/player_name_display"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_marginTop="16dp"
        android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
        android:paddingVertical="8dp"
        android:background="@drawable/player_name_background"
        android:text="L. MESSI"
        android:textColor="#FFFFFF"
        android:textSize="16sp"
        android:textStyle="bold"
        android:visibility="visible"
        app:layout_constraintTop_toBottomOf="@id/top_hud"
        app:layout_constraintStart_toStartOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent"/>

    <!-- Bottom Controls -->
    <LinearLayout
        android:id="@+id/bottom_controls"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:orientation="horizontal"
        android:padding="20dp"
        app:layout_constraintBottom_toBottomOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintStart_toStartOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent">

        <!-- Left Control Pad -->
        <com.example.efootball.VirtualJoystick
            android:id="@+id/left_joystick"
            android:layout_width="120dp"
            android:layout_height="120dp"
            android:layout_marginEnd="40dp"/>

        <!-- Right Action Buttons -->
        <RelativeLayout
            android:layout_width="0dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_weight="1">

            <!-- Pass Button -->
            <ImageButton
                android:id="@+id/pass_button"
                android:layout_width="60dp"
                android:layout_height="60dp"
                android:layout_marginStart="40dp"
                android:src="@drawable/ic_pass"
                android:background="@drawable/button_circle"
                android:layout_centerVertical="true"/>

            <!-- Shoot Button -->
            <ImageButton
                android:id="@+id/shoot_button"
                android:layout_width="70dp"
                android:layout_height="70dp"
                android:layout_marginEnd="40dp"
                android:src="@drawable/ic_shoot"
                android:background="@drawable/button_circle"
                android:layout_centerVertical="true"
                android:layout_alignParentEnd="true"/>

            <!-- Sprint Button -->
            <ImageButton
                android:id="@+id/sprint_button"
                android:layout_width="50dp"
                android:layout_height="50dp"
                android:src="@drawable/ic_sprint"
                android:background="@drawable/button_circle"
                android:layout_alignParentBottom="true"
                android:layout_centerHorizontal="true"/>

        </RelativeLayout>
    </LinearLayout>

    <!-- Tactical Menu Button -->
    <ImageButton
        android:id="@+id/tactical_button"
        android:layout_width="48dp"
        android:layout_height="48dp"
        android:layout_margin="16dp"
        android:src="@drawable/ic_tactical"
        android:background="@drawable/button_square"
        app:layout_constraintTop_toTopOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf="parent"/>

    <!-- Pause Button -->
    <ImageButton
        android:id="@+id/pause_button"
        android:layout_width="48dp"
        android:layout_height="48dp"
        android:layout_margin="16dp"
        android:src="@drawable/ic_pause"
        android:background="@drawable/button_square"
        app:layout_constraintTop_toTopOf="parent"
        app:layout_constraintStart_toStartOf="parent"/>

</androidx.constraintlayout.widget.ConstraintLayout>


**Required drawable resources:**

1. `field_background.xml` - Green football field gradient
2. `player_name_background.xml` - Semi-transparent rounded rectangle
3. `button_circle.xml` - Circular button with shadow
xml
<!-- button_circle.xml -->
<shape xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:shape="oval">
    <solid android:color="#40FFFFFF"/>
    <stroke android:width="2dp" android:color="#FFFFFF"/>
    <size android:width="60dp" android:height="60dp"/>
</shape>


4. `button_square.xml` - Square tactical/pause buttons
5. Various icons: `ic_pass`, `ic_shoot`, `ic_sprint`, `ic_tactical`, `ic_pause`

**Key Features:**
- Responsive ConstraintLayout
- Top HUD with team info and scores
- Virtual joystick for movement
- Action buttons (pass/shoot/sprint)
- Tactical and pause buttons
- Player name display
- Dark theme background

**Note:** The `VirtualJoystick` is a custom view you'd need to implement for touch-based movement control. For a production app, you'd also want to:
1. Add different layouts for portrait/landscape
2. Implement proper state management
3. Add animation resources
4. Include accessibility labels
5. Add haptic feedback to buttons